## API (server; all except `/api/auth` need session cookie)

- `/api/crm` ‚Äî contacts (FUB import fields: birthday, anniversary, etc.)
- `/api/tasks` ‚Äî team tasks; query: `assigned_to`, `transaction_id`, `due_after`, `due_before`, `transaction_only`
- `/api/transactions` ‚Äî CRUD, parties, activity, checklists, DELETE (delete activity before tasks ‚Äî FK)
- `/api/marketing` ‚Äî calendar posts, platform-goals, birthdays range, birthday-pins
- `/api/checklists` ‚Äî template + template_tasks CRUD (`calendar_nickname`, `default_role`)
- `/api/projects` ‚Äî per-user projects CRUD (`?user_id=`); title + description only
- `/api/user-todos` ‚Äî per-user personal todos CRUD; GET purges completed items older than 7 days
- `/api/team` ‚Äî members + stats; list ordered Tessa ‚Üí Adam ‚Üí Margaret ‚Üí Meredith

